        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You pour positive energy into ordinary stones, granting them temporary magical properties. You can target 1 non-magical stone or sling bullet for every action you use @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.aBQ8ajvEBByv45yz]{Casting this Spell}. The stones must be unattended or carried by you or a willing ally. The stones become <em>+1 striking disrupting @Compendium[pf2e.equipment-srd.MKSeXwUm56c15MZa]{Sling Bullets}</em>. Each stone can be used only once, after which it crumbles to dust.</p>",
